'''Spookality''' '''2024''' is a continuation of the annual [[wikipedia:Halloween|Halloween]]-themed jam held by [[VRChat]]. Highlighting creators on VRChat on the Main Menu and in the VRChat home world.

==Jam Winners==
VRChat hosted an [[Avatars|avatar]] and [[Worlds|world]] jam for Spookality, which ran between October 1, to October 14, 2024. The winners for the avatar, and world categories were announced in a {{VRC link|https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/spookality-2024-winners|blog post}} on their website on October 21.<!-- Winners of jam are listed in ascending order. (1st to last place) -->

===Avatars===
Ten avatars were selected for the winning prize. Twenty-five avatars, in addition to the winners, were showcased for Spookality 2024.

==== This is My Final Form! ====
The theme for the avatar jam is to "create an avatar that makes use of [https://creators.vrchat.com/avatars/animator-parameters/#avatar-scaling-parameters Avatar Scaling Parameters] to change its appearance or functionality at larger and small sizes."<ref name="Spookality 2024 announcement blog"/>

===== Judging criteria =====
* Performance is Medium or better on both PC and Android
* Content MUST be Cross-Platform (PC & Android)
* Theme: Spooky
* Theme: Creative use of scaling (both big and small)
* Overall aesthetics
* Extra Features - toggles customization, etc.

===== Prizes =====
The prize for the avatar category winners were:<ref name="Spookality 2024 official rules">[https://hello.vrchat.com/spookality-2024-rules Spookality 2024 Prizes and Rules]</ref>

* Top 10 avatars receive:
** A one-year gift subscription to [[VRChat+]].
** One Spookality pin set.
*Top 25 avatars are featured in an "Avatar Picker" in the [[VRChat Home]] world.

