===Worlds===
This Spookality had two world jam categories you can participate in, the "'''Fractured Realm'''" category, which has ten winners. And the "'''Spookality Showcase'''" category, which has twenty-five winners. Each category has different themes, judging criteria, and prizes!

====Fractured Realm====
The theme for this world category is to "create a spooky world where one player has a different goal and abilities from the others."<ref name="Spookality 2024 announcement blog" /> Ten worlds have been selected to be showcased under the "Fractured Realm" category in Spookality 2024 for the following reasons:

=====Judging criteria=====
*Users (or teams) must have separate win conditions from each other.
*Content MUST be Cross-Platform (PC & Android).
*Mobile-Friendliness.
**The world should be fully usable on Mobile - text is readable on small screens and 3D navigation & locomotion are minimal.
**Check out our Mobile Best Practices doc.
*Inclusion of Theme - Spookiness.
*Inclusion of Theme - Asymmetry.
*Ease of Use.

=====Prizes=====
The prizes for the world category winners were:<ref name="Spookality 2024 official rules" />

*Top 10 worlds receive:
**A one-year gift subscription to [[VRChat+]].
**One Spookality pin set.
**Worlds featured in a special room in the default Home World and in a special category on the main menu.

