==Makeship collaboration==
VRChat collaborated with Makeship to create a glow-in-the-dark [https://www.makeship.com/products/vrchat-spookality-pin-set enamel pin set], including one "VRChat"-themed pin, and one "Spookality [[VRCat]]"-themed pin. The campaign ran from October 1 to October 30, 2024.

<blockquote>''"Just one more ingredient and my experiment should be complete… hold still VRCat!"''
''"meeeeeeeEEeEoOoOOwWWW"''

''Oh no! VRCat's fallen into one of VRRat's crazy experiments… and just in time for Spookality! Snag this rare bone-ified treat, and add Glow-in-the-Dark Skeleton VRCat to your pin collection. We all know you have one ;)''

''Happy Spookality you ghouls!''

''The VRChat Team''</blockquote>

